### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@bookId = 1

### Get all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Accept: application/json

### Get book by id — happy path
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/{{bookId}}
Accept: application/json

### Get book by id — not found (triggers 404 EntityNotFoundException)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/9999
Accept: application/json

### Create a book — valid
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "publishedYear": 2008
}

### Create a book — missing required fields (triggers 400 validation error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "author": null,
  "publishedYear": 2008
}

### Create a book — publishedYear out of range (triggers 400 validation error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Future Book",
  "author": "Someone",
  "publishedYear": 9999
}

### Update a book — happy path
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code (2nd Ed.)",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "publishedYear": 2025
}

### Update a book — not found (triggers 404 EntityNotFoundException)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/books/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ghost Book",
  "author": "Nobody",
  "publishedYear": 2020
}

### Delete a book — happy path
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/books/{{bookId}}

### Delete a book — not found (triggers 404 EntityNotFoundException)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/books/9999
